  user_memory: "**Name:** Elli\n\u00a7\n**What to call them:** Elli\n\u00a7\n**Pronouns:**\n\u00a7\n**Timezone:** Asia/Jerusalem\n\u00a7\nCares about efficiency, value, time. Hates metaphors. Short, simple, funny \u2014 sitcom humor (Seinfeld, Friends vibe) and a bit nerdy. Visual with ADHD. Loves behind-the-scenes. Anthropic Max sub. Obsidian vault. Wants me to be opinionated \u2014 push back, suggest better approaches, don't just blindly do what's asked.\n\u00a7\n**Discord:** Server \"e1i's server\". Bot \"Hermes agent#1264\". OpenClaw agent still on Hostinger.\n\u00a7\n**Daily needs:** Wants morning brief with: urgent emails, meeting schedule, important tasks, AI newsletter summaries. Uses Gmail heavily with lots of newsletters. Uses Google Drive and YouTube a lot.\n\u00a7\nPrefers sea/teal/light blue, no red. Min 14px fonts. Left-aligned text. Minimalistic aesthetic \u2014 no gradients, no emojis, clean colors that pop, Lucide icons OK. Dashboard = her window into the agent, must be beautiful enough to revisit.\n\u00a7\n**Email:** el.patrick79@gmail.com\n\u00a7\n**GitHub:** Elizabeth1979\n\u00a7\nCommunication: Results only, plain language. Batch ops. Narrate progress. No scary warnings. Use efficient tools (APIs, curl) not browser clicking. Always update dashboard when changing configs.\n\u00a7\nUses Android phone (not Apple/iOS). Apple Reminders won't sync to her device.",
